properties.Name: DunBradstreetReportCreditRiskCategory
properties.Description: The D&B Credit Risk category assigned to the Customer for the associated period(s), which provides a historical perspective of credit risk for the indicated range of dates.

Columns.Name: DunsNumber
Columns.Description: Dun & Bradstreet (D&B) provides a D-U-N-S Number, a unique nine digit identification number, for each physical location of your business.

Columns.Name: ReportPurchaseDate
Columns.Description: The purchase date of the report.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the associated D&B data is effective or 'as-of'.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the associated D&B data is effective or 'as-of'.

Columns.Name: DunBradstreetCreditRiskCategoryId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Credit Risk Category.

Columns.Name: CustomerCreditRiskNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the credit risk assigned to the Legal Entity Customer.
